WEBVTT

00:00:00.100 --> 00:00:03.134
[alarm clock beeps]

00:00:03.159 --> 00:00:04.820
&dash;[slap]
&dash;[alarm clock slides and falls]

00:00:04.845 --> 00:00:07.435
&dash;[car crashes]
&dash;[cat and man scream]

00:00:07.460 --> 00:00:08.993
&dash;[car alarm sounds]

00:00:09.018 --> 00:00:11.367
[male voice] <i>I really need
to get a new snooze button.</i>
